title: "Root --id-only flag: minimal mutation output (id+status) for agent automation loops (GH-195)"
description: "Add a root-level --id-only flag (mirroring --no-changed-fields wiring incl. extractCommandScopedOptions delete) that reduces mutation command output to a minimal stable schema: id, status, and warnings if any. Applies to create/update/close/claim/release/copy and MCP mutation tools. Fixes GitHub issue #195."
